元人民币和2.24亿元人民币。叶飞、刘建勋”是否到会北京是否还有人到会？","index":166,"publicationId":"maoquanji39","articleId":"438fdb24fe"}],"page":{"id":"0677e14206","publicationId":"maoquanji39","articleId":"438fdb24fe","start":69,"end":84}}}},"__N_SSG":true}